Maria Sharapova, Caroline Wozniacki, Sabine Lisicki, Angelique Kerber and Sabine Kerber all attended the opening ceremony of the Porsche Grand Prix Tennis event in Stuttgart .
The women were dressed glamorously as they posed for pictures at the Porsche Arena accompanied by a group of school children .
Serena Williams was the highest profile absentee, admitting she was not ready for the clay court season .